sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as DSP API Server
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant WfCtrl as Workflow Controller<br/>9090/TCP Metrics
    participant Pod as Workflow Step Pod<br/>(argoexec sidecar)
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1: Workflow Execution

    DSP->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>WfCtrl: Watch event: New Workflow<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    WfCtrl->>K8s: Create Pod for workflow step<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>Pod: Pod scheduled & started

    Pod->>K8s: Report status (argoexec)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Pod->>S3: Upload artifacts<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
    S3-->>Pod: Artifact stored

    Pod-->>K8s: Update pod status
    WfCtrl->>K8s: Update Workflow status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 2: Artifact Retrieval

    participant Client as Client / UI

    Client->>K8s: (via Argo Server 2746/TCP)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token/SSO
    Note right of K8s: Argo Server proxies<br/>artifact request
    K8s->>S3: Fetch artifact<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
    S3-->>K8s: Artifact data
    K8s-->>Client: Return artifact<br/>HTTPS/TLS

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 3: Workflow Archival (Optional)

    WfCtrl->>DB: Archive workflow data<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    Note right of DB: TLS configurable
    Client->>K8s: Query archived workflows<br/>(via Argo Server)
    K8s->>DB: Read archived workflows<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    DB-->>K8s: Archived workflow data
    K8s-->>Client: Return results
